{"tid":1054081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大馬22歲男「網上辱伊斯蘭教」監禁十一年","createTime":"2019-03-09T14:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T22:46:11.000Z","uid":202464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04b0ab43664d7a92884388b08229d37454a2b783","tid":1054081,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"22歲的科吉亞（Alister Cogia）承認十項罪名，其中五項關於煽動宗教不和，各判兩年刑期，另外五項有關不當使用網絡，各監禁兩個月，由於刑期將分期執行，令他共要監禁10年10個月。另一認罪被告的案件將明日開審；另外兩人分別否認八項和兩項控罪，正被還柙不准保釋，下月5日提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時香港人「網上辱支那共產黨」要坐監？"},{"pid":"bf8fc369ead20185702fe24d2aabbb0be29880e2","tid":1054081,"uid":239954,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:50:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acde9545c00e842aae45bf1cd37ee732c7f127ba","tid":1054081,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"文字獄已經慢慢殺到香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a193296179b0462fe4ef5eb15f3adbab4916e39e","tid":1054081,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e36ee8da602a47d5950703e04a985b69ae59b43","tid":1054081,"uid":60917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"遲下社會計分會俾啲大陸膠推廣去香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27a872c7fb6e4ac6f45989b448a1bef1548a02a","tid":1054081,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲下社會計分會俾啲大陸膠推廣去香港&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n發配邊疆，去海參威做雪條"},{"pid":"a02868602a5ef9336a83c9f4813b75893288e449","tid":1054081,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f27a872c7fb6e4ac6f4